Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) a-su, All of us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask him this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he really want to fight me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Or does he want to leave\Nthe Road Ponegliffs behind and go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him to pick one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Egghead was in turmoil\Ndue to the dark activities of a traitor.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That traitor was...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,York!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Clash! Shanks vs. Eustass Kid"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,SEVERAL HOURS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay now, I want you to listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble is, the World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...seems to have decided to eliminate\Nnot only Stella but also me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! How annoying!\NIt's unforgivable! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's what they're up to,\NI have a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I need you guys\Nto take care of the nuisances!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I closed the Frontier Dome,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so kill everyone other than me, Stella,\Nand the hostages underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you run amok,\Nthey'll begin to wonder who ordered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If they find out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not strong enough\Nto compete with those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on a show of petrifying me\Nin front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Undo it when no one's looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll tell you the places in the lab\Nthat should be left intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So listen carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So the hunting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Everyone, get on board the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get off of Egghead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,ELBAPH, WAR-LAND, NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Our opponent is Red-Haired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're fighting another\NEmperor of the Sea after beating one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop trembling with excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are high-spirited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The tides that have begun to change\Nare unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Kid Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me even if it means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey y'all, Kid Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our chief is Red-Haired Shanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, underlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't {\i1}croak{\i}... Oh! You {\i1}hop{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain stumbled over his words!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you have a chance\Nto see him-{\i1}ribbit{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.82,On Top,,0,0,0,,FROG-TOES GEROTIN\NCAPTAIN OF THE PUDDLE PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He'f wight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, your dentures!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,FUGA THE ADDENTURER\NBANDMASTER OF THE SOCIAL CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You fool! I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...never ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...let you see Chief-{\i1}chan{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so brave! Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,PURURU THE BRR-RAVE\NPRINCESS OF THE BOURGEOIS PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "Hey"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,--Stay away from us-{\i1}ribbit{\i}!\N--They're Red-Haired's allies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,--I will not be defeated!\N--I thought we were in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean,\Nbut there are some famous ones, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't drop your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter if they're small fries,\NI won't cut corners, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that way! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna set sail soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They went out to stop the enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them to retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the damage is done, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa-whoa, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are {\i1}you{\i} guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let them touch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it means a lot to me you offered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't go out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get off of me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so cold, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--Well...\N--Yeah. Don't leave us behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to this,\Neven an Emperor can't hold his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Chief, are you leaving already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Chief! We finally got to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We just dropped by\Non our way to somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now guys, let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran into a big name\Nbecause we stayed too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,--Summon us anytime!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll repeat myself.\NTell the ships to retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Our allies are famously weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you say that? Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We survived thanks to you!\NWe've been protected by your flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Mind your own longevity\Nmore than your enemies. Crone Oli!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Chief! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so popular, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Don't worry.\NWe'll take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, he is worth 3 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate\Nhow fast young people grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But have their wounds from\Nthe Land of Wano healed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They look fine. They're so ready to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get any updates on Blackbeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's definitely\Nleft the Pirate Island, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he'd show up at the Land of Wano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Info about Captain Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Hongo-{\i1}san{\i}!\NYou're well-prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Keeping loading!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from the South Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He has run wild quite a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How many ships are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some faces\NI've seen on wanted posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who the opponents are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna annihilate them in 10 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...this Damned Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the ship... getting pulled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What can he do with just a cannon-{\i1}ribbit{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't flinch, youf guyfs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how they squawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no business with small fries!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...get in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get wiped away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Red-Haired!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the fleet to spread out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorry and Brogy, get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to port!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be too much damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he saw an ill-fated future...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get wiped away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd expect from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Red-Haired!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Divine Departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more Road Ponegliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more\Nto become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido! Big Mom! Red-Haired!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just old-timey scrubs!\NWe're the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can keep up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who'll become\Nthe King of the Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer, you bastard!\NWhy are you laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boss... Boss!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open your eyes!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kid!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kid-{\i}san{\i1}!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss is not moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer-{\i1}san {\i}went in to cover Boss\Nand got hurt, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We surrender, Red-Haired! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill our boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Emma, bring them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-These are the Road Ponegliffs!\NThis is all we got!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A devastating attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, small humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you point a gun\Nat someone else's hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Be prepared to be attacked yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakoku Sovereignty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At Elbaph in the New World,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Kid Pirates led by Eustass "Captain" Kid\Nwith a bounty of 3 billion berries were...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...destroyed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one! Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the chief of the Red-Hair Pirates\Nand one of the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the man who inspired Luffy\Nto become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on March 9th\Nand likes kimchi fried rice and lobster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was a kid,\Nhe was an apprentice to the Roger Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He and Buggy, who is also an Emperor,\Nhave had an unsavory tie since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanks later formed the Red-Hair Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and stayed at Windmill Village\Nin the East Blue for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There, he met Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy wanted to live freely like Shanks\Nand decided to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanks lost his left arm saving Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And he left his straw hat with Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come bring it back to me someday!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once you've become a great pirate!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:23:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy is now a great pirate\Nwho is also one of the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.71,0:23:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Will they be reunited soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Punk Records can predict that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koby becomes a decoy and tries to escape\Nin order to free slaves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}on the Pirate Island of Beehive.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pirates from all over the island\Ncome attacking to block his way!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will Koby, alone and helpless,\Nbe able to do what is right{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and pave the way to liberation?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Run, Koby! A Desperate Escape Strategy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
